instructions: Take the charger off the plate
Put the napkin on the plate
Put the dinner fork next to the plate
Put the salad fork next to the dinner fork
Put the dinner knife next to the plate on the unoccupied side<br><br>
Put the tea spoon next to the dinner knife
Put the soup spoon next to the tea spoon
Put the water glass in front of the plate
Put the wine glass next to the water glass
Move the wine glass down and towards the soup spoon
Put the coffee cup next to the wine glass
Put the bread plate in front of the forks
Put the butter knife on the bread plate
Put the dessert fork in front of the plate
Put the dessert spoon under the dessert fork
